Installation Instructions:

To install our chess program, first start your computers linux
terminal. Then exract the file by typing the command:
                tar -xvzf  ZotMate_Alpha_src.tar.gz
After extracting the file, go into the bin directory ("cd bin")
where you'll be able to access the game. You can make sure the file is
executable by typing "chmod +x Zotmate".
Now type "make all" and afterwards do "./Zotmate"
Congradulations, you have successfuly installed and ran
Zotmate.
In order to acces our sorce code, go in the src directory ("cd src"). There
you may freely view our code. Any concerns regarding the legality's of using
our code can be found in the COPYRIGHT.txt file. 
